%N A015024 Inverse of 1015th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015024 Periodic with period length 1015. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015024 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015024/b015024.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015024 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1015.
%H A015024 <a href="/index/Rec#order_672">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 672.
